      its&nbsp;<a href="content_history.html">history</a> or the
      <a href="content_log.html">log of changes</a> and bugs.
    </p>
    <h2>Hello World</h2>
    <p>This is a simple hello-world.yab written in yabasic, complete with the resulting screenshot:
    <p>  <pre>
	clear screen
	print "Press 'q' to quit ..."
	label again
	print color("green") "Hello ";
	print color("blue") "World !   ";
	if (inkey$(1)="q") exit
	goto again
    </pre></p>
    <p><img src="hello-world.png" width="50%"></p>
